2002-2013 (La. 10/25/02)

Julie STEED v. UNITED SERVICES AUTOMOBILE ASSOCIATION. No. 2002-CC-2013. Supreme Court of Louisiana. Oct. 25, 2002.

In re Steed, Julie; — Plaintiff; Applying for Supervisory and/or Remedial Writs, Parish of Jefferson, 24th Judicial District *1159Court Div. M, No. 555-670; to the Court of Appeal, Fifth Circuit, No. 2002-C-570.

Denied.

CALOGERO, C.J., would grant the writ.
